{"tid":1836042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全新嘅實景體驗遊戲《Biohazard XI Wuhan City》終於推出啦！","createTime":"2020-01-23T05:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T20:02:01.000Z","uid":77018,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3195fd0a993e0ca2bcd3aa1e88fc4d28aba7eba","tid":1836042,"uid":77018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnpdRaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnpdRaZ.jpg&h=3a406160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4D14dpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4D14dpj.jpg&h=e44b1d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由Chincom推出全新嘅實景體驗遊戲《Biohazard XI Wuhan City》終於推出啦！<br />\n玩家會係遊戲中扮演成第一日上任既警察習昂或者尋找兄長既嘉莉，<br />\n於因冠状病毒而封鎖舞汗市入面，開槍打死曬所有唔聽話，公開疫情嘅感染者！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Djyx6KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjyx6KC.jpg&h=5a3dd232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢款遊戲唔需要購買任何主機都可以玩，<br />\n只要你有一顆心「爱国心」，去西九龍有一間叫做「羔鐵」既Game鋪，<br />\n問果到D職員點去遊戲場景「舞汗」，就會有專人教路帶你點去！<br />\n<br />\n值得一提隻Game今日10點果陣就完左封測，聽聞已經有幾十萬數個玩家已經離開左舞汗，<br />\n因為簽左保密協議既關係，建議各位不論是否玩家都應該常帶口罩，以免禍從口出！"},{"pid":"4903818622e296b9c18672b3b3fff699cc9e6896","tid":1836042,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXt98Yd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXt98Yd.png&h=711715ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5ab2c2bf356fd5d39e05c18763bbe1921a118e2","tid":1836042,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3195fd0a993e0ca2bcd3aa1e88fc4d28aba7eba","tid":1836042,"uid":77018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnpdRaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnpdRaZ.jpg&h=3a406160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i